-- Ukraine rebels say to hand black boxes to Malaysia experts at 1900 GMT
-- 
-- Mon Jul 21, 2014 01:12PM EDT
-- None



DONETSK, Ukraine, July 21 (Reuters) - Separatists in eastern Ukraine will hand over the black boxes from a downed airliner to Malaysian experts at 1900 GMT on Monday, Sergei Kavtaradze, an official of the rebels' self-proclaimed Donetsk People's Republic, told Reuters.   (Reporting by Anton Zverev, writing by Gabriela Baczynska, editing by Elizabeth Piper)  ((elizabeth.piper@thomsonreuters.com)(+74957751242)(Reuters Messaging: elizabeth.piper.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: UKRAINE CRISIS/BLACKBOXES

